\section{Formatting progress lines}

The list command should be scannable.  One line per tutorial is enough if
we include both the tutorial ID and its current progress summary.

<<functions>>=
def format_progress_line(title: str, progress: ProgressState, summary: str) -> str:
    """Return one display line for the list command."""

    status = (
        "completed"
        if progress.finished
        else f"{progress.completed_steps}/{progress.total_steps} complete"
    )
    return f"{title}: {status} - {summary}"
@

<<test functions>>=
